      class="text-orange-500 dark:text-orange-400"
      href="https://www.learninpublic.org/"
      target="noopener"
      >learn in public</a>.
    </p>
  <p>
    <i>
      <strong>{{ pagination.items.length }}</strong> TILs and counting...</i>
  </p>
</p>

<p class="mb-12">
    You can follow along by watching my <a
      class="text-orange-500 dark:text-orange-400"href="https://github.com/petermekhaeil/til">GitHub repository<a/>.
